xword (1.0.5) stable; urgency=low

  * Added new Preference menu option to set the minimum box size (between
    12 and 40 inclusive)
  * Added two new buttons on the keyboard toolbar for "check word" and
    "solve word"

 -- Terrence Fleury <terrencegf@gmail.com>  Tue, 22 Apr 2008 17:05:00 -0500

xword (1.0.4) stable; urgency=low

  * Replaced xkbd with a built-in keyboard.  The new keyboard is actually 
    several toolbars.  The user can select to view the keyboard on the
    Left/Right, the old check buttons toolbar on the Left/Right, or neither
  * F7,F8 (-/+ buttons on N8x0) now do previous / next word
  * Escape does "check word"
  * Fixed scroll window bug where clicking on a cell when the puzzle 
    window is scrolled results in the incorrect cell being selected
  * Clicking on th the current "red' cell changes direction
  * Uploaded all of the icon files to the garage.maemo.org svn

 -- Terrence Fleury <terrencegf@gmail.com>  Fri, 18 Apr 2008 11:28:00 -0500

